{"id":5683,"date":"2022-09-19T09:02:23","date_gmt":"2022-09-19T01:02:23","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.acclime.com\/?page_id=5683"},"modified":"2023-07-06T16:15:21","modified_gmt":"2023-07-06T08:15:21","slug":"boardmanagement","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.acclime.com\/agility\/boardmanagement\/","title":{"rendered":"BoardManagement"},"content":{"rendered":"<h1>Acclime BoardManagement<\/h1>\n<h2>Secure board management software for corporates<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h2>\n<div>\n<p>Acclime BoardManagement is a secure collaboration platform purpose-built for directors to organise meetings, manage and securely share sensitive documents, communicate and&nbsp;make&nbsp;decisions.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p>\n    <a href=\"https:\/\/meetings.hubspot.com\/a-garcia13\/acclimeboardmanagement\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Schedule a personalised demo<\/a>\n<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/acclime-boardmanagement-dashboard.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2>Practical board management solution for various types of corporations<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h2>\n<div>\n<p>Acclime BoardManagement provides a full set of tools to organise meetings and manage materials and tasks throughout the entire meeting lifecycle. Directors can collaborate and access up-to-date information securely, in real-time, and from any device.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/eor-1.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3>For directors, CEOs &#038;&nbsp;executives<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h3>\n<div>\n<p>Prepare for board meetings with ease and confidence. Collaborate securely, and access the latest information in real-time from any device. Make the board\u2019s decision-making process more effective.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/operational-support.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3>For company secretaries &#038;&nbsp;board administrators<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h3>\n<div>\n<p>Spend less time on routine administrative tasks of board meetings. Use the full suite of online tools for organising meetings, and manage all board and committee documents and communications.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/checkbox.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3>Simple<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h3>\n<div>\n<p>BoardManagement has focused, straightforward yet powerful features. Get things done on your board more efficiently and effectively without a learning curve.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/hr-payroll.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3>Affordable<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h3>\n<div>\n<p>Single per-user subscription fee that covers everything. No add-on modules, implementation or training fees. Start from as few as five users and scale as\u00a0needed.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/privacy-1.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3>Secure<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h3>\n<div>\n<p>Enterprise data security and privacy built-in from day one. The platform is <strong>ISO27001<\/strong>-certified, <strong>GDPR-compliant<\/strong> with client data exclusively hosted in the European Union.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Drive your board to action<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h2>\n<div>\n<p>Acclime BoardManagement makes meetings more effective and engaging for the board. By streamlining meeting workflows and removing administrative distractions, directors can focus on important matters and make quicker, smarter decisions that lead to better outcomes.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div>\n<h3>Streamline all your board meeting administration tasks<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h3>\n<div>\n<p>Replace manual processes and the need to work across multiple apps. You can schedule meetings, track tasks, create agendas, compile your digital board packs and take minutes all within Acclime BoardManagement.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/screen-streamline-meeting.webp\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<div>\n<h3>Protect sensitive information from unauthorised access and data breaches<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h3>\n<div>\n<p>Sharing board information through channels such as email attachments exposes you to security risks. By placing sensitive information on a highly-secure and encrypted platform that\u2019s independent from the rest of the organisation, you mitigate risks of data breaches and cyber attacks.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/screen-protect-information.png\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<div>\n<h3>Secure single source and version of truth for the board<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h3>\n<div>\n<p>When everyone works with updated and accurate information, a greater amount of trust is placed on the data. As the central hub for board information, Acclime BoardManagement makes decision-making more insightful and efficient.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/screen-single-source-of-truth.webp\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<div>\n<h3>Collaborate, govern, meet and&nbsp;work anywhere<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h3>\n<div>\n<p>Directors can review materials, look up board records, collaborate with others as well as sign documents from anywhere. Board duties and decision-making are no longer restricted to board meetings and inside boardrooms.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/screen-collaborate-anywhere.webp\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<div>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/customer-support.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2>First-class services &amp;&nbsp;client&nbsp;support<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h2>\n<div>\n<p>Acclime BoardManagement is an intuitive, simple to manage and easy-to-use board portal. Setup is effortless and requires minimal to no user training. But we want to ensure you get the most out of our platform. From day one, our team of specialist company secretarial &amp; corporate governance professionals will be ready to help you implement the solution, so it becomes immediately effective for your board and processes.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h4><span class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-image dot-alignment\" style=\"background-image: url(\/wp-content\/uploads\/dot.svg); width: 15px;\"><\/span> Free implementation<\/h4>\n<div>\n<p>Our free implementation plan is tailored to the specific needs of your board. We work with you to design this plan. The transition to Acclime BoardManagement is easy and seamless.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<h4><span class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-image dot-alignment\" style=\"background-image: url(\/wp-content\/uploads\/dot.svg); width: 15px;\"><\/span> Unlimited training<\/h4>\n<div>\n<p>We provide unlimited, virtual, personalised training sessions for your administrators at no extra cost.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<h4><span class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-image dot-alignment\" style=\"background-image: url(\/wp-content\/uploads\/dot.svg); width: 15px;\"><\/span> First-class support<\/h4>\n<div>\n<p>If you need help, our team is only a call or an email away.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/privacy-1.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2>Best-in-class security<br class=\"uk-visible@m\"> for your sensitive&nbsp;data<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h2>\n<div>\n<p>Sharing board-level information through traditional channels such as email attachments and printouts exposes organisations to security risks. Acclime BoardManagement provides a highly-secure platform where all sensitive data can&nbsp;be managed and shared.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/check.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<div>Scalable and reliable cloud architecture <\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/check.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<div>Regular penetration testing\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/check.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<div>Granular access permissions\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/check.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<div>Full data and system ownership\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/check.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<div>GDPR compliant<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/check.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<div>VeraSafe privacy certified\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/check.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<div>Biometric authentication<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/check.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<div>Disable devices remotely<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/check.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<div>Regular backups and disaster recovery<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/vera-safe.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3>vera-safe<\/h3>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.acclime.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/gdpr.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3>iso-27001<\/h3>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/iso-27001.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3>iso-27001<\/h3>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><iframe src=\"https:\/\/vimeo.com\/751102667\"><\/iframe><\/p>\n<div>\n<h2>Advance in Asia with&nbsp;a complete tech&#8209;enabled solution<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h2>\n<div>\n<p>Agility is Acclime\u2019s complete cloud-based system to <strong>view, track and exchange documents<\/strong> for convenient collaboration, corporate administration and efficient management of every aspect of your corporate governance across Asia.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p><a href=\"\/agility\/\">Learn more<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/agility.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2>Modernise your corporate governance today.<\/h2>\n<p>\n    <a href=\"https:\/\/meetings.hubspot.com\/a-garcia13\/acclimeboardmanagement\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Schedule a personalised demo<\/a>\n<\/p>\n<p><!--more--><br \/>\n<!-- {\"type\":\"layout\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"section\",\"props\":{\"animation\":\"slide-bottom-small\",\"animation_delay\":\"150\",\"css\":\".el-section {background: linear-gradient(to top, #FBCDA6, #FDE6D2);}\\n\\\/*.el-section {background-color: #FBCDA6;}*\\\/\\n\",\"image_position\":\"bottom-center\",\"image_size\":\"width-1-1\",\"padding_remove_bottom\":true,\"style\":\"default\",\"title_breakpoint\":\"xl\",\"title_position\":\"top-left\",\"title_rotation\":\"left\",\"vertical_align\":\"middle\",\"width\":\"\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"row\",\"props\":{\"column_gap\":\"medium\",\"margin\":\"default\",\"width\":\"xsmall\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"column\",\"props\":{\"image_position\":\"center-center\",\"position_sticky_breakpoint\":\"m\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"headline\",\"props\":{\"class\":\"acc-orange\",\"content\":\"Acclime BoardManagement\",\"margin\":\"small\",\"text_align\":\"center\",\"title_element\":\"h1\",\"title_style\":\"h5\"}},{\"type\":\"headline\",\"props\":{\"block_align\":\"center\",\"content\":\"Secure board management software for corporates<span class=\\\"acc-orange\\\">.<\\\/span>\",\"margin\":\"default\",\"maxwidth\":\"2xlarge\",\"text_align\":\"center\",\"title_element\":\"h2\",\"title_style\":\"h1\"}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"props\":{\"block_align\":\"center\",\"class\":\"uk-h4\",\"column_breakpoint\":\"m\",\"content\":\"\n\n<p>Acclime BoardManagement is a secure collaboration platform purpose-built for directors to organise meetings,